  "title": "Food Processing Worker",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Support day-to-day operations in the production section.</li><li>Follow standard operating procedures for basic food preparation.</li><li>Store food properly in the correct containers and storage areas to prevent spoilage.</li><li>Keep the production area clean, tidy, and hygienic at all times.</li><li>Follow all food hygiene and safety standards.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Friendly and pleasant personality.</li><li>Able to prioritise tasks well.</li><li>Able to take initiative and work independently when needed.</li><li>Positive attitude and willing to learn.</li><li>Comfortable working in a fast-paced environment and can adapt quickly.</li></ul>",
